Name: Living and Flaming Catastrophes (I)
Desc: When the same ally acts consecutively, they receive 1 stack of Memory Imprint. When allies with Memory Imprint attack, every Memory Imprint stack has a <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> fixed chance to inflict the target with Dissociation that lasts for 1 turn. Allies with Memory Imprint deal <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#3[i]%</unbreak></color> more DMG. This effect cannot be stacked. When a different ally acts, remove all Memory Imprint stacks on the field.\nDissociation: This state is considered as the Freeze state. Affected units cannot take action. When this state is removed, the affected target receives Additional Ice DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak></color> of their respective Max HP.

Challenge.Name: Win with at least <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> Cycle(s) left
Win with at least <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> Cycle(s) left
Have no downed characters
